\frac{1}{r}=\frac{1}{R}+\underbrace{\frac{xx'+yy'+zz'}{R^{3}}}_{=\frac{\vec{R}\cdot\vec{R}'}{R^{3}}}+\frac{1}{2}\sum_{i=1}^{3}\sum_{j=1}^{3}\frac{3x_{i}x_{j}-\delta_{ij}R^{2}}{R^{5}}x'_{i}x'_{j}+\dots=
\]

