 vector 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{\delta}$
\end_inset

, forzosamente debe ser:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{\nabla}\Omega=\oint_{C}\frac{d\vec{l}\times\vec{r}}{r^{3}}
\]

\end_inset

Y en consecuencia:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{E}=\frac{\tau}{4\pi\varepsilon_{0}}\oint_{C}\frac{d\vec{l}\times\vec{r}}{r^{3}}
