W_{2}=w_{1}+w_{2}=q_{2}\phi_{21}=q_{2}\frac{1}{4\pi\varepsilon_{0}}\frac{q_{1}}{r_{12}}=\frac{1}{2}\left(\frac{1}{4\pi\varepsilon_{0}}\frac{q_{1}q_{2}}{r_{12}}+\frac{1}{4\pi\varepsilon_{0}}\frac{q_{1}q_{2}}{r_{12}}\right)
